Hello! I'll be in NYC for 6 months while doing an internship with AAM. If you are in NYC then you should be my friend. Goals: Make friends who enjoy bike riding and listening to good music. Find cute boy that I can date longer than a month. Learn to properly navigate NYC. Never be late to work. Network my ass off. ...more goals to come I'm sure....
Tomorrow I will see all the people I have separated myself from this past year. This is going to end badly.
I am super into dance music recently. If you would please send me your favorite dance albums that would be much appreciated. I'll also take some requests!

8. trips to nyc are a must. someone wanna come with me? i need to see my best friend.
i miss him dearly. bergs stop being mia.

10. i can't get enough of dance music. i think i'll marry dan deacon or some who will listen to dan deacon 24/7 with me and dance.

kbye. love you. you are super.

Last night I had a dream that someone had been breaking into my car and leaving my friend's dead bodies in my car with threatening notes that were written in blood. The attornies at the office were trying to help me figure out who was doing it. The killer would slash the throats and stomachs of his/her victims with a huge knife ensuring instant death. The killer was clearly after me but everyone kept protecting me but the killer was too efficient and always killed my protectors.  Every single one of my bristol friends died in my dream, along with everyone at my work place. My friends from northeastern then came to help me solve the horrifying mystery. The killer seemed to be no where to be found but suddenly he/she appeared and then right before my little brother was about to be killed Annie jumped on the killers back and Jason shoved a saw through the killers stomach. The dead killer was unveiled and ended up being one of my coworkers whom I hate hate hate hate. This dream had many more details than what I'm writing here but even though it was just a dream I feel that it was quite symbolic. I have a couple ideas of what it could be but leave me a comment and let me know what you think.

This Thursday I'm seeing Via Audio with Josh and then Saturday I'm seeing Thunderbirds are now! but I think I'm going by myself. Oh well it's gonna be a SICK concert and it's at TT the bears and I really like that venue so I'm wicked excited. I also found out today that I have NO FINALS so my xmas vacation starts on December 6th, but I'm not going home till the 8th becuase Murder By Death is the 7th and I'm going to that one for free! :0) I don't like Bristol but I'm excited to be going home for breaks because I'm starting to get lonely here and missing my friends back home. I need a cuddle buddy here at school desperately.

I have no idea what to name it!
Suggestions?

yeah, so i never update. whatever.
anyway, i got a single for next year which i have mixed feelings about. i dont mind having a single but i kinda wanted a room mate for the experience. im on the "leadership" floor for some reason, i dont remember asking for themed housing but oh well. im also in speare hall which isnt the nicest dorm but it isnt bad. its across from the dining halls and close to marino, so we'll see how things work out. feel free to visit me next year!

Yeah, i'm pretty positive im getting a macbook. Everyone I've talked to has loved it and I have been given $1,900 to spend on a computer so I might as well. Plus I'm pretty good at getting viruses so hopefully this will cut down on that. Thanks for the input!

DELL Laptop or a Macbook?
Yeah, I can't decide between Apple and Windows. 
I'm leaning towards Apple.
Opinions?

What the fuck Morningstar!? All I ask of you is to make me delicious veggie burgers, I never asked for you to put a free sample fajita burger in the box of veggie burgers. I was looking forward to eating your delicious product, but you had to ruin it by tricking me into eating your free sample. Honestly, if I wanted a fajita burger I would have bought them. Next time I eat a veggie burger it better be straight veggies, none of this fajita buisness. So fuck you Morningstar! If you plan on putting free samples in the box I recommend that you LABEL it a little better.
